item.itunes:title: Starship Athena
item.description:
Today we quickly look at whether or not you can die from lack of sleep, explore the health benefits of nicotine, and take a trip to Starship Athena.

Patreon
https://www.patreon.com/user?u=18482113

MERCH STORE!!!
https://tinyurl.com/y8zam4o2

Nicotine actually has many health benefits, from preventing Parkinson's to giving your brain a boost. But is their a healthy way to take it?

Then, we meet the Arcturians who guard Earth from evil aliens. They pilot the Starship Athena which is considered the most powerful starship in the galaxy. Are they the reason why we don't have disclosure?
